version 0.6
-----------

features:

- framework:

    + GfxComponent
    + GfxShape
        *GfxRectangle
    + GfxText
    + GfxImage

    + basic SWF and GIF target creation
    + NO animation

    SWF:
    + links for GfxImage
    + shadows for GfxRectangle, GfxImage and GfxText
    + strokes for GfxRectangle and GfxImage

    SWF/GIF:
    + source images may be jpeg, gif, png

- editor:

    + almost every feature editable now (still missing font size selection)
    + full REST API connection implemented
    + layout due to rework

- generator script:

    + mass generation of banners (both GIF and SWF) based on product feeds by company



